snippet.title: Intellivania (Intellivision, 2019)
snippet.description:
Castlevania-like game for Intellivision by Matthew Kiehl. Impressive feat for console 5 years older than MSX where Castlevania appeared originally. The demo contains 2 levels, but only managed to get to first boss.

I downloaded this demo from Atariage at http://atariage.com/forums/topic/288155-demo-playable-preview-intellivania;-castlevania-on-intellivision/
